Package io.cyborgcode.roa.ui.selenium.logging

Class LoggingFunctions

java.lang.Object
io.cyborgcode.roa.ui.selenium.logging.LoggingFunctions
public class LoggingFunctions extends Object
Provides logging functions for exception handling during Selenium WebDriver interactions. This class logs detailed information for various exceptions encountered while performing actions such as finding elements, clicking, sending keys, and submitting forms.
